<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>GrowWise | Lead Generation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 40px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    nav a {
      margin: 0 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      background-color: #2d8a48;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
    }
    .hero-text {
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero img {
      max-width: 300px;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .features {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .features h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .feature-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .feature {
      max-width: 250px;
    }
    .feature img {
      height: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .contact {
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      background: #f0f0f0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">
    <img src="growwise-logo.png" alt="GrowWise Logo" />
    <strong>GrowWise</strong>
  </div>
  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="#">Services</a>
    <button class="cta-btn">Contact</button>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h1>Generate More Leads and Grow Your Business</h1>
    <p>Our lead generation strategies help you reach new customers and increase revenue.</p>
    <button class="cta-btn">Get Started</button>
  </div>
  <img src="growwise-icon.png" alt="Growth Icon" />
</section>

<section class="features">
  <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="icon-strategy.png" alt="Strategy Icon" />
      <h3>Proven Strategies</h3>
      <p>We use effective and tested strategies to generate high-quality leads for your business.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="icon-expert.png" alt="Expert Icon" />
      <h3>Expert Team</h3>
      <p>Our experienced professionals are dedicated to helping your business grow.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="icon-gear.png" alt="Gear Icon" />
      <h3>Customized Solutions</h3>
      <p>We tailor our lead generation services to meet your unique needs.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="contact">
  <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
  <p>Contact us today to learn how we can help your business grow.</p>
  <button class="cta-btn">Contact Us</button>
</section>

<footer>
  &copy; 2025 GrowWise. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
